profile:
Since 1994, A Village Fireplace Shop has been your one-stop location for all fireplace, barbeque and outdoor leisure product needs. With the recent addition of a heating and cooling division, A Village Fireplace Shop has become your complete 
Home Comfort specialist.
Fireplaces: Boasting a showroom with over 40 working gas, wood and electric models
Barbeques: Large selection of Canadian-made premium Napoleon barbeques
Outdoor Leisure Products: High quality hammocks, swings, rockers and umbrellas for those warm summer days!
Heating and Cooling: Energystar-rated Tappan furnaces and air conditioners for low operating costs plus the best warranties in the industry!
Standby Generators: Enjoy peace of mind knowing that if the power goes out, your Generac standby generator restores power within seconds and immediately shuts down once power is restored to the home
name: A Village Fireplace Shop
